Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,낯선 천장이다...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,아!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,정신이 들었어?
