Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,아아...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 전혀\N아무렇지도 않아요...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨가 쓰러졌다길래\N걱정했지 뭐야!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,죄..죄송해요...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,억...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,무슨 일 있어?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 아뇨...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어..어쩌지?
