Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그..그래도!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}니지카쨩도
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내가 후회 안 하는 쪽으로\N결정하면 될 거라고 해줬구...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}폭망하기라도 했다간
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}고등학교 생활을\N견디지 못할 거 같기도 하구...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}라이브 하우스에서의 연주도\N긴장돼서 막 버벅이는데
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}문화제 스테이지는\N무슨...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}응!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}역시 안 되지~
