Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}네!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}설마 그 고토 씨가\N밴드를 했었다니...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}사인 받아둘 걸\N그랬어~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}목표는\N이쪽 노선으로 가자!
