Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}고민도 해소됐네~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다행이고♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,좋은 아침!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 어...\N안녕하세요...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,몸 상태는 어때?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,어제 걱정돼서\N보건실에 돌아가봤더니
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨는\N이미 없더라구
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,에!?\N아, 그랬나요...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,죄송해요...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,아!\N그리고 내가 내뒀어!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,잉?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,문화제 때\N개인 스테이지!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,결속밴드로\N출연할 거지!?
