Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,사운드를 들으라고
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,사운드를!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,료 선배...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,SICK HACK은\N어떤 밴드예요?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,장르는\N사이키델릭 Rock
